{"tid":1162314,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"抄歌永遠只有MR自己知 有定冇","createTime":"2019-05-19T19:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T04:16:13.000Z","uid":16785,"like":7,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6e04428e2361b58893a09da3585b5bb3f371f46b","tid":1162314,"uid":16785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T19:43:26.000Z","msg":"老實講<br />\n抄歌永遠只有MR自己知 有定冇<br />\n外人聽落即使99.9%似<br />\n都永遠冇可能知作曲人係咪100%抄<br />\n作曲人好可能憑空作個melody出嚟<br />\n點知就撞到應一應<br />\n音樂就係一樣咁嘅<br />\n<br />\n一味淨屌MR抄歌嘅人<br />\n只會愈顯得你睇野有幾咁慮淺<br />\n永遠只單靠個人感覺去批判他人。<br />\n<br />\n我同你地啲haters講<br />\n假如首歌99.9%似<br />\n姐係仲有0.1%嘅可能佢唔係抄<br />\n如果咁就判死罪。<br />\n萬一佢地係嗰0.1%<br />\n姐係佢哋係原創。<br />\n咁就死咗隊好band.<br />\n<br />\n而且唔好淨係茅指MR.<br />\n一首歌有監制，發行，仲有公司<br />\n全部都覺得冇問題先推出<br />\n要屌就屌埋其他<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n對一個Mr fans嚟講<br />\n係得零時起閧，Mr Tam呢兩首爭議性好大<br />\n其他根本冇抄<br />\n而且抄呢個行為涉及人格品題。<br />\n經過多年嘅支持，了解Mr<br />\n同埋琴晚Alan唱不屈嗰滴眼淚。<br />\n我幾肯定佢哋冇諗過要對住一首歌嚟抄。<br />\n更加冇動機去抄<br />\n<br />\n對我而言<br />\n呢兩隻歌極為相似外國巨band名作嘅原因<br />\n只係佢地製作上嘅巨大失誤<br />\n並唔係所謂嘅抄<br />\n<br />\n明就明。"},{"pid":"c91f9b2794b446e17867bce480b2ae073efcbb17","tid":1162314,"uid":16785,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T19:45:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rk-rc6o97xg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRk-rc6o97xg&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ1%2F1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=2c42121c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Rk-rc6o97xg</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9SKFwtgUJHs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9SKFwtgUJHs&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ1%2F1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=eee1431a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9SKFwtgUJHs</a><br />\n明耳人一聽就知唔係抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d0c5d398c3d26cc1abcedba0a8d2b38dfb76e8","tid":1162314,"uid":16785,"like":